org.sakaiproject.sms.hibernate.model
Class SmsMessage

java.lang.Object
  org.sakaiproject.sms.hibernate.model.BaseModel
      org.sakaiproject.sms.hibernate.model.SmsMessage

public class SmsMessage
extends BaseModel

A single sms message. One or more messages is linked to a sms task. When a task is future dated (e.q.: send message x to group x and date z). It's messages will only be inserted on the date the task must execute.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Julian Wyngaard
